    },
    {
      "id": "feqyJlh_7HhWTPXfRgh9g",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1960,
      "y": 1060,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "-GgEE2kROYtEKiK9LQ62a"
      ],
      "frameId": "wOzEezyojffBefVHAZ87N",
      "index": "b0VzzzzzzzzzzzzzzlO",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1366295941,
      "version": 334,
      "versionNonce": 55386047,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782160491312,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Обозначение p+ область содержит\nмного акцепторных примесей и\nхорошо проводит за счёт дырок.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Обозначение p+ область содержит много акцепторных примесей и хорошо проводит за счёт дырок.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "rYzQLVfxuktzAvWUFb4A5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1640,
      "y": 1060,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 60,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "-GgEE2kROYtEKiK9LQ62a"
      ],
      "frameId": "wOzEezyojffBefVHAZ87N",
      "index": "b0VzzzzzzzzzzzzzzlV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1049694411,
      "version": 389,
      "versionNonce": 2070216625,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782160491312,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Обозначение n+ область содержит\nмного донорных примесей и хорошо\nпроводит за счёт электронов.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Обозначение n+ область содержит много донорных примесей и хорошо проводит за счёт электронов.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bGg2CnMWGOTvzhbazxX8P",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1640,
      "y": 1020,
      "width": 620,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "-GgEE2kROYtEKiK9LQ62a"
      ],
      "frameId": "wOzEezyojffBefVHAZ87N",
      "index": "b0VzzzzzzzzzzzzzzlZ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1819315173,
      "version": 437,
      "versionNonce": 422629343,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782160491312,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Обозначения n+ и p+ означают сильное легирование.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Обозначения n+ и p+ означают сильное легирование.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "IrtddbyyH4d0DAVLadRUM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1640,
      "y": 1140,
      "width": 619.9999999999999,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "-GgEE2kROYtEKiK9LQ62a"
      ],
      "frameId": "wOzEezyojffBefVHAZ87N",
      "index": "b0Vzzzzzzzzzzzzzzld",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 439383845,
      "version": 328,
      "versionNonce": 1793843601,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782160491312,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. GND (Ground) - точка отсчёта напряжения, логический 0.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. GND (Ground) - точка отсчёта напряжения, логический 0.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "V3MbtpTLz7i7Vr2pcx-GE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1640,
      "y": 1180,
      "width": 620.0000000000001,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "-GgEE2kROYtEKiK9LQ62a"
      ],
      "frameId": "wOzEezyojffBefVHAZ87N",
      "index": "b0Vzzzzzzzzzzzzzzll",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 744116396,
      "version": 139,
      "versionNonce": 1936292863,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782160491312,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3. VDD (Voltage at the Drain) – положительная шина питания, логическая 1.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3. VDD (Voltage at the Drain) – положительная шина питания, логическая 1.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
